                  throws Exception
        Records a test run
        Parameters:
        testerUserId - The user id of the person who's running the test (null for logged in user)
        testCaseId - The test case being executed
        releaseId - The release being executed against (optional)
        testSetId - The test set being executed against (optional)
        executionStatusId - The status of the test run (pass/fail/not run)
        runnerName - The name of the automated testing tool
        runnerTestName - The name of the test as stored in JUnit
        runnerAssertCount - The number of assertions
        runnerMessage - The failure message (if appropriate)
        runnerStackTrace - The error stack trace (if any)
        endDate - When the test run ended
        startDate - When the test run started
        Throws:
        Exception
